OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FLargely dry over the next few days
OL,7,Fwith variable amounts of cloud and
OL,8,Fsunny spells. A few showers are
OL,9,Fpossible on Wednesday. Very warm in
OL,10,Fthe sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
